<p>Primary goal for the listing page was to provide coherent hierarchy and concise information organization. After listing out all the components on the current app, I crossed off some that seemed unnecessary and labeled them by priority. Highest priority, to my knowledge when using the app, was the gas price. Users want to know which gas station has the lowest price. Other key components were name, distance, payment method, and location.</p>

